he best photographs from the games, a dozen of their photographers shared their favorite images along with the stories of how each was captured.\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their staff\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"their favorite images\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"stories\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 442}, {\"ngram\": \"the\\u00c2first\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 493}, {\"ngram\": \"a final roundup\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"the best photographs\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"a dozen\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"their photographers\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"their favorite images\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"the stories\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To capture this image, I utilized one of the glass screens on a scoreboard at the foot of the beam.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this image\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"the glass screens\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"a scoreboard\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"the foot\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 752}, {\"ngram\": \"the beam\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a challenging shot because I had to align the beam perfectly for the composition to work.\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a challenging shot\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"the beam\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"the composition\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I positioned my camera directly along the scoreboard screen, and everything came together beautifully.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my camera\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"the scoreboard screen\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovering a new angle or approach to capture a sport is always exciting and having the chance to photograph Simone was amazing.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new angle\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She wore a white leotard that day, which stood out perfectly against the black stadium background.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a white leotard\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the black stadium background\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a shot I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m really proud of.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"a shot\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve attempted this type of shot before with different apparatus at various gymnastics events.\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this type\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"shot\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"different apparatus\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"various gymnastics events\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the first few days in Paris, I looked for this opportunity, but the scoreboard screens weren\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t facing the right way until that particular day.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1358, \"end\": 1363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999989986944694, \"rank\": 1.001306482041448e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first few days\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"this opportunity\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"the scoreboard screens\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"the right way\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"that particular day\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I saw there was TV in that spot, I seized the opportunity to try it!\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"that spot\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone struggles sometimes, but it's how one handles themselves.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Michelle Jenneke of Team Australia took a fall in the Women's 100m Hurdles Round 1 heat, she could have easily walked off the track.\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\", \"score\": 0.9978275636412803, \"rank\": 0.002127868918214142, \"text\": \"Michelle\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Obama\"}, {\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999994412440143, \"rank\": 5.587562875895091e-07, \"text\": \"Team Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fall\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"the Women's 100m Hurdles Round 1 heat\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she kept pushing to finish the race, ultimately still struggling.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her perseverance and determination to do so inspires more than those winning gold which makes an image such as this graphic one so memorable.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her perseverance\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"an image\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"this graphic one\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the beginning of every session, the venue would play a light show prior to the event starting.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"every session\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"a light show\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had photographed it in a few other ways that did not really showcase what they were displaying.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few other ways\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, on this day I took a different approach and broke out a lens I very, very rarely use.\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this day\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"a different approach\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2213}, {\"ngram\": \"a lens\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it sensed like the right opportunity to use it in the corner of the track, creating this beautiful-looking image with vibrant colors and movement.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right opportunity\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"the corner\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"this beautiful-looking image\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"vibrant colors\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"movement\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was my first time shooting beach volleyball at an Olympic Ganes.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first time\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"beach volleyball\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Ganes\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I saw the promotional video for the Paris Olympics, I was amazed by the scenery of beach volleyball and knew it would make for some compelling images both during the day and especially at night.\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the promotional video\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"the scenery\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"beach volleyball\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2586}, {\"ngram\": \"some compelling images\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The shooting challenge with beach volleyball was to follow the rules and not move freely during the competition, so I chose to shoot in the media stand in the first round of the game and then return to the ground.\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2895, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The shooting challenge\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"beach volleyball\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2726}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2750}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2864}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using a wide-angle lens to wait for the perfect moment, I was able to capture athletes while the Eiffel Tower was in the background.\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 3028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a wide-angle lens\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2919}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect moment\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3005}, {\"ngram\": \"the background\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eiffel Tower, Olympic rings and Paris 2024 branding all over the venue, provide a picturesque backdrop for all the emotion, action and beauty happening throughout the competition and will be photos that we look back on for years to come.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3065, \"end\": 3075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999929867971424, \"rank\": 7.013694745720669e-05, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3045}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic rings\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3103}, {\"ngram\": \"a picturesque backdrop\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"all the emotion\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3155}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3163}, {\"ngram\": \"beauty\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3174}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3211}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For reasons that were not very clear to us, the medal ceremony was held off to the side of the pitch behind the goal area.\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reasons\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3283}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3314}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal ceremony\", \"from\": 3316, \"to\": 3334}, {\"ngram\": \"the side\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3359}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3372}, {\"ngram\": \"the goal area\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Normally, the ceremony is held in the middle of the pitch facing the main grandstand, with photographers placed on the middle of the sideline.\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3537, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3417}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3439}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3452}, {\"ngram\": \"the main grandstand\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3479}, {\"ngram\": \"photographers\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3520}, {\"ngram\": \"the sideline\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year though the photographers had to stand off to the sides and or over the other side of the pitch, which is where I chose to capture this image with a 400mm lens.\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the photographers\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"the sides\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3602}, {\"ngram\": \"the other side\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3629}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3642}, {\"ngram\": \"this image\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3688}, {\"ngram\": \"a 400mm lens\", \"from\": 3694, \"to\": 3706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This posed another challenge with the Spider Camera dropping down and blocking most of my shots, but wanted to focus on getting Team USA celebrating their gold medal win with fans in the background.\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3836, \"end\": 3844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.6737041457431298, \"rank\": 0.27005754843165736, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another challenge\", \"from\": 3719, \"to\": 3736}, {\"ngram\": \"the Spider Camera\", \"from\": 3742, \"to\": 3759}, {\"ngram\": \"my shots\", \"from\": 3795, \"to\": 3803}, {\"ngram\": \"their gold medal\", \"from\": 3857, \"to\": 3873}, {\"ngram\": \"win\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3877}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3887}, {\"ngram\": \"the background\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can see the varied emotions of the players taking in the moment.\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 3975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the varied emotions\", \"from\": 3919, \"to\": 3938}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3953}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 3974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the Men's 3000m Steeplechase, I had the opportunity to place the camera in the steeplechase water obstacle.\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 4088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Men's 3000m Steeplechase\", \"from\": 3981, \"to\": 4009}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4032}, {\"ngram\": \"the camera\", \"from\": 4042, \"to\": 4052}, {\"ngram\": \"the steeplechase water obstacle\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It enables you to capture a unique image and angle of the athletes as they jump over the hurdle and the water.\", \"from\": 4089, \"to\": 4199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a unique image\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"angle\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4139}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 4143, \"to\": 4155}, {\"ngram\": \"the hurdle\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4184}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 4189, \"to\": 4198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also illustrates how close together they are and the precision with which they are able to jump even when running at 100% I used a 10-20mm lens and Canon R5 in a Nauticam underwater housing.\", \"from\": 4200, \"to\": 4393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100%\", \"from\": 4320, \"to\": 4324}, {\"ngram\": \"a 10-20mm lens\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4346}, {\"ngram\": \"a Nauticam underwater housing\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What a night!\", \"from\": 4395, \"to\": 4408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have probably covered over 1000+ basketball games in my career, but I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t think any of them have been as exciting as this one.\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1000+ basketball games\", \"from\": 4438, \"to\": 4460}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 4464, \"to\": 4473}, {\"ngram\": \"don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t\", \"from\": 4481, \"to\": 4488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My favorite athlete to photograph of all time is Steph Curry, and he was playing great that night.\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4591, \"end\": 4602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steph Curry\", \"types\": [\"Q