, {\"sentence\": \"When the buzzer went off, he went running out onto the court, and it was great to see how excited he was.\", \"from\": 4885, \"to\": 4990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the buzzer\", \"from\": 4890, \"to\": 4900}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 4936, \"to\": 4945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fact that the Serbian player was lying on the ground and fans were holding up a giant USA sign in the background definitely helped the picture.\", \"from\": 4991, \"to\": 5138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5009, \"end\": 5016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_language\", \"score\": 0.5756196333708239, \"rank\": 0.595763192816503, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 5081, \"end\": 5084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9382657770067534, \"rank\": 0.052828064315060846, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 4991, \"to\": 4999}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 5037, \"to\": 5047}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5056}, {\"ngram\": \"the background\", \"from\": 5093, \"to\": 5107}, {\"ngram\": \"the picture\", \"from\": 5126, \"to\": 5137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been working with the team at Getty Images who for nine months have been thinking about projects to try to have an approach to the Olympic Games from another perspective.\", \"from\": 5140, \"to\": 5317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5177, \"end\": 5182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999935570743411, \"rank\": 4.6741287957351494e-06, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images