e\": \"Kristiansen and Herrem for Team Norway epitomized the way their side had gone about the business of overcoming their Scandinavian rivals.\", \"from\": 5884, \"to\": 6021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kristiansen\", \"from\": 5884, \"to\": 5895}, {\"ngram\": \"Herrem\", \"from\": 5900, \"to\": 5906}, {\"ngram\": \"Team Norway\", \"from\": 5911, \"to\": 5922}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 5934, \"to\": 5941}, {\"ngram\": \"their side\", \"from\": 5942, \"to\": 5952}, {\"ngram\": \"the business\", \"from\": 5968, \"to\": 5980}, {\"ngram\": \"their Scandinavian rivals\", \"from\": 5995, \"to\": 6020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In many ways, there are far more exciting shots from the match but I was looking for an opportunity to highlight the level of commitment Norway gave versus the struggle of Denmark.\", \"from\": 6022, \"to\": 6202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6159, \"end\": 6165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9859947931646997, \"rank\": 0.013298122462248365, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 6194, \"end\": 6201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.7718530380854797, \"rank\": 0.26876921340177123, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many ways\", \"from\": 6025, \"to\": 6034}, {\"ngram\": \"far more exciting shots\", \"from\": 6046, \"to\": 6069}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 6075, \"to\": 6084}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 6107, \"to\": 6121}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 6135, \"to\": 6144}, {\"ngram\": \"commitment\", \"from\": 6148, \"to\": 6158}, {\"ngram\": \"the struggle\", \"from\": 6178, \"to\": 6190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was able to pivot onto this shot as the players turned towards me and if you look at the expressions of the three athletes you have the narrative of the game.\", \"from\": 6203, \"to\": 6363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this shot\", \"from\": 6228, \"to\": 6237}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 6241, \"to\": 6252}, {\"ngram\": \"the expressions\", \"from\": 6290, \"to\": 6305}, {\"ngram\": \"the three athletes\", \"from\": 6309, \"to\": 6327}, {\"ngram\": \"the narrative\", \"from\": 6337, \"to\": 6350}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 6354, \"to\": 6362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s nice when my impression of the game which I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m looking to capture comes together with a moment to give an overall perspective in a single shot.\", \"from\": 6364, \"to\": 6515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 6364, \"to\": 6370}, {\"ngram\": \"my impression\", \"from\": 6381, \"to\": 6394}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 6398, \"to\": 6406}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 6413, \"to\": 6418}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 6458, \"to\": 6466}, {\"ngram\": \"an overall perspective\", \"from\": 6475, \"to\": 6497}, {\"ngram\": \"a single shot\", \"from\": 6501, \"to\": 6514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Olympics is my second time photographing table tennis.\", \"from\": 6517, \"to\": 6586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6527, \"end\": 6540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my second time\", \"from\": 6544, \"to\": 6558}, {\"ngram\": \"table tennis\", \"from\": 6573, \"to\": 6585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the Tokyo 2020 Games, I covered all 14 days of competition so I am now quite familiar with the sport and some of the athlete's tendencies, which can come as an advantage when anticipating action.\", \"from\": 6587, \"to\": 6789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo 2020 Games\", \"from\": 6594, \"to\": 6614}, {\"ngram\": \"all 14 days\", \"from\": 6626, \"to\": 6637}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 6641, \"to\": 6652}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 6685, \"to\": 6694}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's tendencies\", \"from\": 6707, \"to\": 6731}, {\"ngram\": \"an advantage\", \"from\": 6751, \"to\": 6763}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 6782, \"to\": 6788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A challenging part of photographing is the backgrounds aren\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t always the cleanest.\", \"from\": 6790, \"to\": 6874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A challenging part\", \"from\": 6790, \"to\": 6808}, {\"ngram\": \"photographing\", \"from\": 6812, \"to\": 6825}, {\"ngram\": \"the backgrounds\", \"from\": 6829, \"to\": 6844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The key is to find a spot where the light falls off enough to create a dark background away from referees, LED boards, and other distracting components.\", \"from\": 6875, \"to\": 7027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The key\", \"from\": 6875, \"to\": 6882}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 6894, \"to\": 6900}, {\"ngram\": \"the light\", \"from\": 6907, \"to\": 6916}, {\"ngram\": \"a dark background\", \"from\": 6944, \"to\": 6961}, {\"ngram\": \"referees\", \"from\": 6972, \"to\": 6980}, {\"ngram\": \"LED boards\", \"from\": 6982, \"to\": 6992}, {\"ngram\": \"other distracting components\", \"from\": 6998, \"to\": 7026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The venue has field of play positions so you can get fairly close to the athletes along the sides of the table.\", \"from\": 7028, \"to\": 7139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The venue\", \"from\": 7028, \"to\": 7037}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 7042, \"to\": 7047}, {\"ngram\": \"play positions\", \"from\": 7051, \"to\": 7065}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 7097, \"to\": 7109}, {\"ngram\": \"the sides\", \"from\": 7116, \"to\": 7125}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 7129, \"to\": 7138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I prefer to sit on the ground instead of designated photo benches because the lower my line of sight is, the cleaner my backgrounds become.\", \"from\": 7140, \"to\": 7279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 7159, \"to\": 7169}, {\"ngram\": \"designated photo benches\", \"from\": 7181, \"to\": 7205}, {\"ngram\": \"the lower my line\", \"from\": 7214, \"to\": 7231}, {\"ngram\": \"sight\", \"from\": 7235, \"to\": 7240}, {\"ngram\": \"my backgrounds\", \"from\": 7257, \"to\": 7271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This picture turned out particularly well while the female peloton was passing in a big bunch and making the image very colorful in combination with the blue sky and neutral colors of the Louvre Museum\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a main landmark in Paris, making this a must have picture.\", \"from\": 7281, \"to\": 7543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7504, \"end\": 7509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999991101457775, \"rank\": 8.898550619185727e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This picture\", \"from\": 7281, \"to\": 7293}, {\"ngram\": \"the female peloton\", \"from\": 7329, \"to\": 7347}, {\"ngram\": \"a big bunch\", \"from\": 7363, \"to\": 7374}, {\"ngram\": \"the image\", \"from\": 7386, \"to\": 7395}, {\"ngram\": \"combination\", \"from\": 7413, \"to\": 7424}, {\"ngram\": \"the blue sky\", \"from\": 7430, \"to\": 7442}, {\"ngram\": \"neutral colors\", \"from\": 7447, \"to\": 7461}, {\"ngram\": \"the Louvre Museum\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a main landmark\", \"from\": 7465, \"to\": 7500}, {\"ngram\": \"picture\", \"from\": 7535, \"to\": 7542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The priority was to get there early to secure the central photo position, which also helped make it completely symmetric with the Louvre building in the background.\", \"from\": 7544, \"to\": 7708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7674, \"end\": 7680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"score\": 0.9999246297355894, \"rank\": 7.537593412231681e-05, \"text\": \"Louvre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The priority\", \"from\": 7544, \"to\": 7556}, {\"ngram\": \"the central photo position\", \"from\": 7590, \"to\": 7616}, {\"ngram\": \"the background\", \"from\": 7693, \"to\": 7707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not every day we get to see such clean image without anything else around, especially in summer where this area is normally overwhelmed by tourists.\", \"from\": 7709, \"to\": 7864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such clean image\", \"from\": 7744, \"to\": 7760}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 7769, \"to\": 7777}, {\"ngram\": \"summer\", \"from\": 7805, \"to\": 7811}, {\"ngram\": \"this area\", \"from\": 7818, \"to\": 7827}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 7855, \"to\": 7863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being in more than one place at once is physically possible.\", \"from\": 7866, \"to\": 7926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than one place\", \"from\": 7875, \"to\": 7894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, a remote camera, triggered by a radio from another place, allows for this in photography.\", \"from\": 7927, \"to\": 8025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a remote camera\", \"from\": 7936, \"to\": 7951}, {\"ngram\": \"a radio\", \"from\": 7966, \"to\": 7973}, {\"ngram\": \"another place\", \"from\": 7979, \"to\": 7992}, {\"ngram\": \"photography\", \"from\": 8013, \"to\": 8024}]}, {\"sentence\": 