to\": 10243}, {\"ngram\": \"dark moody sky\", \"from\": 10247, \"to\": 10261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As much as the Olympic Games are about covering the action and the pinnacle of the sport, I find that taking wide scenic pictures is such an important thing to do at every venue I visit as these are the pictures that people will look back on when remembering the Games for what they were.\", \"from\": 10263, \"to\": 10551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 10274, \"to\": 10291}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 10311, \"to\": 10321}, {\"ngram\": \"the pinnacle\", \"from\": 10326, \"to\": 10338}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 10342, \"to\": 10351}, {\"ngram\": \"wide scenic pictures\", \"from\": 10372, \"to\": 10392}, {\"ngram\": \"such an important thing\", \"from\": 10396, \"to\": 10419}, {\"ngram\": \"every venue\", \"from\": 10429, \"to\": 10440}, {\"ngram\": \"the pictures\", \"from\": 10462, \"to\": 10474}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 10480, \"to\": 10486}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 10522, \"to\": 10531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This photo was shot with a remote camera.\", \"from\": 10553, \"to\": 10594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This photo\", \"from\": 10553, \"to\": 10563}, {\"ngram\": \"a remote camera\", \"from\": 10578, \"to\": 10593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I positioned the camera in this location two hours before the event started.\", \"from\": 10595, \"to\": 10671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the camera\", \"from\": 10608, \"to\": 10618}, {\"ngram\": \"this location\", \"from\": 10622, \"to\": 10635}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 10653, \"to\": 10662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I sought to not only show the sport but the atmosphere surrounding the entire sport in such a beautiful venue.\", \"from\": 10672, \"to\": 10782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 10698, \"to\": 10707}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmospher