inal, the rain started coming down making the track look like glass which made for something a bit different.\", \"from\": 11179, \"to\": 11321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rain\", \"from\": 11218, \"to\": 11226}, {\"ngram\": \"the track look\", \"from\": 11254, \"to\": 11268}, {\"ngram\": \"glass\", \"from\": 11274, \"to\": 11279}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 11295, \"to\": 11304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the final was happening, I took a quick look up at the TV screen to see if anyone was clearly in front.\", \"from\": 11322, \"to\": 11428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a quick look\", \"from\": 11357, \"to\": 11369}, {\"ngram\": \"the TV screen\", \"from\": 11376, \"to\": 11389}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 11400, \"to\": 11406}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 11422, \"to\": 11427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson was a hot favorite to take out the 100m however I saw Julien Alfred was in the lead.\", \"from\": 11429, \"to\": 11524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11429, \"end\": 11439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.7771108568803919, \"rank\": 0.2868176716196297, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hot favorite\", \"from\": 11444, \"to\": 11458}, {\"ngram\": \"Julien Alfred\", \"from\": 11494, \"to\": 11507}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 11515, \"to\": 11523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Making a split decision to change and focus on her paid off as she celebrated well over the line with rain bouncing off her and the track.\", \"from\": 11525, \"to\": 11663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a split decision\", \"from\": 11532, \"to\": 11548}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 11613, \"to\": 11621}, {\"ngram\": \"rain\", \"from\": 