\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Triple_jump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Triple_jump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Maryna Bekh\", \"from\": 13547, \"to\": 13558}, {\"ngram\": \"Romanchuk\", \"from\": 13559, \"to\": 13568}, {\"ngram\": \"Team Ukraine\", \"from\": 13572, \"to\": 13584}, {\"ngram\": \"the assignment\", \"from\": 13640, \"to\": 13654}, {\"ngram\": \"compelling images\", \"from\": 13675, \"to\": 13692}, {\"ngram\": \"different vantage points\", \"from\": 13698, \"to\": 13722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One often thinks sitting in the 'cheap seats' does not make for a great image, but with the light setting quickly, I was able to make a dynamic image, showing the power of the athlete.\", \"from\": 13724, \"to\": 13908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 'cheap seats\", \"from\": 13752, \"to\": 13768}, {\"ngram\": \"a great image\", \"from\": 13788, \"to\": 13801}, {\"ngram\": \"the light\", \"from\": 13812, \"to\": 13821}, {\"ngram\": \"a dynamic image\", \"from\": 13858, \"to\": 13873}, {\"ngram\": \"the power\", \"from\": 13883, \"to\": 13892}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 13896, \"to\": 13907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was using our new underwater robotic camera to capture this image and am able to frame up to capture a few different boards.\", \"from\": 13910, \"to\": 14036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our new underwater robotic camera\", \"from\": 13922, \"to\": 13955}, {\"ngram\": \"this image\", \"from\": 13967, \"to\": 13977}, {\"ngram\": \"a few different boards\", \"from\": 14013, \"to\": 14035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is important to have a basic knowledge of diving as you need to know which direction the athlete will travel when they hit the water.\", \"from\": 14037, \"to\": 14173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a basic knowledge\", \"from\": 14061, \"to\": 14078}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 14082, \"to\": 14088}, {\"ngram\": \"which direction\", \"from\": 14109, \"to\": 14124}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 14125, \"to\": 14136}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 14163, \"to\": 14172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think this angle really illustrates the speeds and the impact with which they hit the water, usually capturing different shapes and emotions of the athletes underwater.\", \"from\": 14174, \"to\": 14344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this angle\", \"from\": 14182, \"to\": 14192}, {\"ngram\": \"the speeds\", \"from\": 14212, \"to\": 14222}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 14227, \"to\": 14237}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 14258, \"to\": 14267}, {\"ngram\": \"different shapes\", \"from\": 14287, \"to\": 14303}, {\"ngram\": \"emotions\", \"from\": 14308, \"to\": 14316}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 14320, \"to\": 14332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For this composition of the 100m final for a project called \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cLayers of the Games\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d, I visited the photo positions that the organization gave us the day before.\", \"from\": 14346, \"to\": 14508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this composition\", \"from\": 14350, \"to\": 14366}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 14370, \"to\": 14378}, {\"ngram\": \"a project\", \"from\": 14389, \"to\": 14398}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cLayers\", \"from\": 14406, \"to\": 14415}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 14419, \"to\": 14431}, {\"ngram\": \"the photo positions\", \"from\": 14443, \"to\": 14462}, {\"ngram\": \"the organization\", \"from\": 14468, \"to\": 14484}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 14490, \"to\": 14492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I decided that this position on the second floor of the stadium could work quite well for what I had in mind.\", \"from\": 14509, \"to\": 14622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this position\", \"from\": 14528, \"to\": 14541}, {\"ngram\": \"the second floor\", \"from\": 14545, \"to\": 14561}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 14565, \"to\": 14576}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 14617, \"to\": 14621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An elevated position helps me to be able to see the different stages of the competition.\", \"from\": 14623, \"to\": 14711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An elevated position\", \"from\": 14623, \"to\": 14643}, {\"ngram\": \"the different stages\", \"from\": 14671, \"to\": 14691}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 14695, \"to\": 14710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The camera has to be in the same location in all the shots, so I fix it with a clamp to some structure in the stadium or the stands.\", \"from\": 14712, \"to\": 14844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The camera\", \"from\": 14712, \"to\": 14722}, {\"ngram\": \"the same location\", \"from\": 14736, \"to\": 14753}, {\"ngram\": \"all the shots\", \"from\": 14757, \"to\": 14770}, {\"ngram\": \"a clamp\", \"from\": 14789, \"to\": 14796}, {\"ngram\": \"some structure\", \"from\": 14800, \"to\": 14814}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 14818, \"to\": 14829}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 14833, \"to\": 14843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After this comes the editing process where I join the different moments layer by layer to be able to have this result.\", \"from\": 14845, \"to\": 14963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the editing process\", \"from\": 14862, \"to\": 14881}, {\"ngram\": \"the different moments layer\", \"from\": 14895, \"to\": 14922}, {\"ngram\": \"layer\", \"from\": 14926, \"to\": 14931}, {\"ngram\": \"this result\", \"from\": 14951, \"to\": 14962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the case of the photo of the 100m final, there were only eight photos and therefore eight different layers.\", \"from\": 14964, \"to\": 15074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 14967, \"to\": 14975}, {\"ngram\": \"the photo\", \"from\": 14979, \"to\": 14988}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 14992, \"to\": 15000}, {\"ngram\": \"only eight photos\", \"from\": 15019, \"to\": 15036}, {\"ngram\": \"therefore eight different layers\", \"from\": 15041, \"to\": 15073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in other sports such as soccer, up to almost 100 different layers were used.\", \"from\": 15075, \"to\": 15155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 15082, \"to\": 15094}, {\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 15103, \"to\": 15109}, {\"ngram\": \"almost 100 different layers\", \"from\": 15117, \"to\": 15144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The editing work has been challenging because I try to take care of the details and see relevant moments of the competitions.\", \"from\": 15156, \"to\": 15281, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The editing work\", \"from\": 15156, \"to\": 15172}, {\"ngram\": \"care\", \"from\": 15216, \"to\": 15220}, {\"ngram\": \"the details\", \"from\": 15224, \"to\": 15235}, {\"ngram\": \"relevant moments\", \"from\": 15244, \"to\": 15260}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 15264, \"to\": 15280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the fieldwork at the locations has also been important because if I have a good position, it will help the editing to be more fluid and much more interesting when it comes to seeing the details of each photo.\", \"from\": 15282, \"to\": 15494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fieldwork\", \"from\": 15286, \"to\": 15299}, {\"ngram\": \"the locations\", \"from\": 15303, \"to\": 15316}, {\"ngram\": \"a good position\", \"from\": 15359, \"to\": 15374}, {\"ngram\": \"the editing\", \"from\": 15389, \"to\": 15400}, {\"ngram\": \"the details\", \"from\": 15468, \"to\": 15479}, {\"ngram\": \"each photo\", \"from\": 15483, \"to\": 15493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Due to the static nature of archery, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s important to look around your venue as much as possible to try and find alternative angles of the athletes competing as you know where and when they will be in action.\", \"from\": 15496, \"to\": 15707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the static nature\", \"from\": 15503, \"to\": 15520}, {\"ngram\": \"archery\", \"from\": 15524, \"to\": 15531}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 15533, \"to\": 15539}, {\"ngram\": \"your venue\", \"from\": 15565, \"to\": 15575}, {\"ngram\": \"alternative angles\", \"from\": 15612, \"to\": 15630}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 15634, \"to\": 15646}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 15700, \"to\": 15706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This frame was taken from outside of the main competition arena and over on the practice facility at 800mm.\", \"from\": 15708, \"to\": 15815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This frame\", \"from\": 15708, \"to\": 15718}, {\"ngram\": \"the main competition arena\", \"from\": 15745, \"to\": 15771}, {\"ngram\": \"the practice facility\", \"from\": 15784, \"to\": 15805}, {\"ngram\": \"800mm\", \"from\": 15809, \"to\": 15814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took a lot of time and patience as the picture only worked first thing in the morning when the sun was low.\", \"from\": 15816, \"to\": 15926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 15824, \"to\": 15829}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 15833, \"to\": 15837}, {\"ngram\": \"patience\", \"from\": 15842, \"to\": 15850}, {\"ngram\": \"the picture\", \"from\": 15854, \"to\": 15865}, {\"ngram\": \"first thing\", \"from\": 15878, \"to\": 15889}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 15893, \"to\": 15904}, {\"ngram\": \"the sun\", \"from\": 15910, \"to\": 15917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another factor was a remote TV camera which was constantly moving in front of the shot, so to get this frame eventually felt very satisfying.\", \"from\": 15927, \"to\": 16068, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another factor\", \"from\": 15927, \"to\": 15941}, {\"ngram\": \"a remote TV camera\", \"from\": 15946, \"to\": 15964}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 15996, \"to\": 16001}, {\"ngram\": \"the shot\", \"from\": 16005, \"to\": 16013}, {\"ngram\": \"this frame\", \"from\": 16025, \"to\": 16035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 also gives the photo a nice sense of place.\", \"from\": 16069, \"to\": 16127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16073, \"end\": 16083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999996045517, \"rank\": 3.954507849870484e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the photo\", \"from\": 16095, \"to\": 16104}, {\"ngram\": \"a nice sense\", \"from\": 16105, \"to\": 16117}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 16121, \"to\": 16126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This picture was taken during the first training session when the US team was at the competition venue.\", \"from\": 16129, \"to\": 16232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16195, \"end\": 16197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9827071785719886, \"rank\": 0.012195214977804647, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This picture\", \"from\": 16129, \"to\": 16141}, {\"ngram\": \"the first training session\", \"from\": 16159, \"to\": 16185}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition venue\", \"from\": 16210, \"to\": 16231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The uneven bars always make for interesting, eye-catching images when the women leap from bar to bar.\", \"from\": 16233, \"to\": 16334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The uneven bars\", \"from\": 16233, \"to\": 16248}, {\"ngram\": \"interesting, eye-catching images\", \"from\": 16265, \"to\": 16297}, {\"ngram\": \"the women\", \"from\": 16303, \"to\": 16312}, {\"ngram\": \"bar\", \"from\": 16323,