-300 f2.8 zoom.\", \"from\": 16611, \"to\": 16695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new lens\", \"from\": 16628, \"to\": 16638}, {\"ngram\": \"a 100-300 f2.8 zoom\", \"from\": 16675, \"to\": 16694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This lens is incredible, and the combination of the lens and camera can track the eyes of the athletes like never before and make the picture tack sharp.\", \"from\": 16696, \"to\": 16849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This lens\", \"from\": 16696, \"to\": 16705}, {\"ngram\": \"the combination\", \"from\": 16725, \"to\": 16740}, {\"ngram\": \"the lens\", \"from\": 16744, \"to\": 16752}, {\"ngram\": \"camera\", \"from\": 16757, \"to\": 16763}, {\"ngram\": \"the eyes\", \"from\": 16774, \"to\": 16782}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 16786, \"to\": 16798}, {\"ngram\": \"the picture\", \"from\": 16826, \"to\": 16837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was able to focus on Jordan Chiles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 eyes when she jumped from beam to beam to make this image \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 like she is looking right at us.\", \"from\": 16850, \"to\": 16984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16873, \"end\": 16879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.8670707143551867, \"rank\": 0.08132465724699696, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"beam\", \"from\": 16916, \"to\": 16920}, {\"ngram\": \"this image\", \"from\": 16937, \"to\": 16947}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 16981, \"to\": 16983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is one of my favorite shots from the Games, but I think I might be slightly more attached to it as it was something I have been wanting to try and capture for a long time and have only just been able to start trying, due to the huge advances we have made with our underwater robotic.\", \