g at relatively slow shutter speeds.\", \"from\": 17462, \"to\": 17561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the speed\", \"from\": 17489, \"to\": 17498}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimmers\", \"from\": 17502, \"to\": 17514}, {\"ngram\": \"relatively slow shutter speeds\", \"from\": 17530, \"to\": 17560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think the slower shutter gives a slightly painterly effect and dreamlike quality.\", \"from\": 17562, \"to\": 17645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the slower shutter\", \"from\": 17570, \"to\": 17588}, {\"ngram\": \"a slightly painterly effect\", \"from\": 17595, \"to\": 17622}, {\"ngram\": \"dreamlike quality\", \"from\": 17627, \"to\": 17644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love trying to capture images that can alter your mood slightly and that you maybe can not digest in the first instant you see it but needs a little longer to sink in.\", \"from\": 17646, \"to\": 17815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"images\", \"from\": 17671, \"to\": 17677}, {\"ngram\": \"your mood\", \"from\": 17693, \"to\": 17702}, {\"ngram\": \"the first instant\", \"from\": 17749, \"to\": 17766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marie Eve Gahie of Team France reacts after losing her match at Judo, for this I was just looking to document the athletes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 emotions leaving the mat, whatever it may be, and in this case, the devastation was clear on her face.\", \"from\": 17817, \"to\": 18045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17823, \"end\": 17826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve\", \"score\": 0.5984490010810081, \"rank\": 0.5199737794955384, \"text\": \"Eve\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve\"}, {\"begin\": 17836, \"end\": 17847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_France\", \"score\": 0.9998281868617057, \"rank\": 0.0001718197183488377, \"text\": \"Team France\", \"types\": [], \"wik